	                            <h2>We are the ITviec VIPs</h2>
	                            <p>Our mission is to help awesome developers like you grow your IT career.</p>
	                            <p>We do this by featuring great IT jobs from top companies. And we offer you content and resources you need to move up to your next IT job.</p>
	                            <p>We don&#8217;t have the most IT jobs &#8212; just the best ones.</p>
	                            <p>60 Nguyen Van Thu, Da Kao Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam
	                                <br /> (+84) 08-6681-1397
	                                <br /> itviec@itviec.com
	                            </p>
